      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how much pain you're in, and I want to reassure you that your feelings of hopelessness are valid and understandable in this moment. You don't need to justify your pain to anyone, and you deserve support that meets you exactly where you are without judgment. Please consider reaching out to a crisis support line like 988 in the US, which offers compassionate, non-judgmental listening for anyone in deep distress.",
